high_descs: Turn left for five steps, turn left for eight steps, turn right for one step and stop in front of the coffee machine.
Pick up the coffee mug from the machine.
Turn left for five steps, turn right for one step to to face the sink.
Put the cup in the sink, turn on the water for a couple seconds to rinse the cup, turn off the water and take the cup out of the sink.
Turn right for five steps, turn left to face the coffee machine.
Put the coffee cup back on the coffee machine where you first took it.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed coffee cup on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn left, move forward, turn left again, and move toward the coffee machine on the right.
Pick up the dirty coffee cup from the coffee machine.
Turn left and head toward the kitchen sink on the right.
Put the dirty coffee cup in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn right and head back over to the coffee machine on the left.
Put the clean coffee cup back on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean coffee cup on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn to the left, go forward to the garbage can, hang a left, go to the counter on the right where the coffee maker is.
Pick up the mug that is on the coffee maker.
Turn to the left, go forward to the sink that is on the right.
Put the mug in the sink and rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Turn to the right, go forward to the coffee maker that is on the left.
Put the mug back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug on the coffee maker.
